---
---
<section class="relative w-full bg-brand-walnut-dark md:h-screen md:min-h-[680px] md:overflow-hidden">

  <!-- MOBILE: image stacked on top -->
  <div class="relative w-full h-[60vh] min-h-[360px] overflow-hidden md:hidden bg-brand-walnut-dark">
    <img
      src="/images/hero-cropped.webp"
      alt="TIMBRCase — a hand-built birch ITX PC case"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-contain"
      style="object-position: center center;"
      fetchpriority="high"
    />
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1/4 bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-walnut-dark to-transparent"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- DESKTOP: image as full-bleed background -->
  <img
    src="/images/hero-cropped.webp"
    alt=""
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="hidden md:block absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-contain"
    style="object-position: 73% center; transform: scale(0.9);"
  />

  <div class="hidden md:block absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-2/5 bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-walnut-dark via-brand-walnut-dark/60 to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="hidden md:block absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-walnut-dark/70 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="hidden md:block absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(circle at 70% 35%, rgba(238,189,104,0.18), transparent 55%);"></div>

  <!-- TEXT: stacked below on mobile, overlaid on desktop -->
  <div class="relative z-10 px-6 py-14 md:absolute md:inset-0 md:px-0 md:py-0 md:flex md:items-end md:pb-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto md:px-12 w-full">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <span class="inline-block text-xs tracking-[0.32em] uppercase mb-6 font-semibold motion-safe:animate-[fadeUp_0.9s_ease-out_0.1s_both]" style="color:#c98855; text-shadow:0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.55);">
          European wood · Hand-built in Germany
        </span>
        <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl leading-[1.02] mb-7 motion-safe:animate-[fadeUp_1s_ease-out_0.25s_both]">
          The PC case<br/>
          <span class="italic text-gradient-gold">that feels<br/>like furniture.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-cream/75 max-w-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed font-light motion-safe:animate-[fadeUp_1s_ease-out_0.45s_both]">
          Most PCs hide — under desks, pretending they don't exist. TIMBRCase is the opposite: a small, quiet, solid-birch case, adding warmth and a calming energy to your space.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 motion-safe:animate-[fadeUp_1s_ease-out_0.6s_both]">
          <a href="#reserve" class="px-7 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-brand-purple text-brand-cream font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
            Choose Your TIMBRCase
          </a>
          <a href="/about" class="px-7 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-brand-gold text-brand-walnut-dark font-semibold hover:bg-brand-gold-bright transition-colors">
            About TIMBRCase
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<style>
  @keyframes heroDrift {
    0%, 100% { transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0); }
    50%      { transform: translate3d(-0.5%, -0.5%, 0); }
  }
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
</style>
